科學研究寫作                            


  	This course is intended for International students in the Nursing Department Master’s Program. This course will help the students further refine their scientific reasoning skills in conjunction with basic skills of scientific communication in an English academic environment as they work on their written (and oral) research proposals. 

課程教育目標 

A. 養成進階護理專業人才(Advanced Practice Nurse-APN) 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[基本素養]國際視野。
[核心能力]應用批判性思考模式，展現問題解決能力。
批判性思考應用研究方法分析及介入護理實務問題。
護理研究展現自我導向學習規劃專業生涯。
